赞达亚谈《幸福感》第三季：“时间跳跃正在发生” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendaya-on-euphoria-season- Three-the-time-jump-is-happening-3799956?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=zendaya-on-euphoria-season-三时跳跃正在发生Poppy BurtonSun, 06 Oct 2024 10:10:49 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3799956 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="赞达亚" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位两届艾美奖得主开玩笑说“你能处理的高中戏剧就这么多”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendaya-on-euphoria-season-three-the-time-jump-is-happening-3799956">Zendaya 在《Euphoria》第三季中发表的帖子：“时间跳跃正在发生”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="赞达亚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/zendaya-emmys-carpet-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">赞达亚</a>已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/euphoria"><em>《幸福感》</em></a>第三季将以时间跳跃为特色。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/heres-what-we-know-about-euphoria-season-three-3223110">这是我们对《幸福感》第三季的了解</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位两届艾美奖得主在剧中扮演鲁·贝内特，最近透露第三部将以时间跳跃为特色，她在<em>《娱乐周刊》的</em><a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/challengers-star-zendaya-fall-festival-recap-and/id1375036030?i=1000671660941" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>颁奖</i></a>播客上表示这“很重要”。</p><p> “因为你能处理的高中戏剧就这么多，”她开玩笑说，并补充道：“然后她又背叛了她的男朋友！”赞达亚还将担任该剧的执行制片人，虽然她无法透露太多细节，但她承诺新的故事情节将“引人入胜”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3224399" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3224399" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3224399" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main.jpg" alt="赞达亚欣快感" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Zendaya-Euphoria-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3224399" class="wp-caption-text">赞达亚在《幸福感》第二季中饰演 Rue Bennett。图片来源：HBO</figcaption></figure><p> “我实际上不太了解正在发生的事情，”她承认。 “我不太清楚这个赛季会是什么样子，但我确实知道时间跳跃正在发生。”</p><p>这位<em>《沙丘》</em>明星继续说道：“在高中背景之外看到和理解这些角色，以及我们在他们小时候和高中时看到的所有东西如何影响他们的成年期以及他们成为谁，这将是一件很有趣的事情。”在一个更大的世界里。我也有兴趣看看会发生什么。”</p><p>同样，扮演卡西·霍华德的西德尼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sydney-sweeney">·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney)</a>在今年早些时候公开了时间跳跃，告诉<a href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/celebs/a61807070/sydney-sweeney-interview-august-2024/"><em>《大都市》，</em></a>这对她来说是“一个新的过程”。</p><p> “我只是边走边学习，并对即将发生的一切持开放态度。但我也很兴奋。我爱卡西。她总是一个令人兴奋的角色，所以我真的很期待她的生活中会发生什么。”</p><p> HBO 电视剧部主管弗朗西斯卡·奥尔西 (Francesca Orsi) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/euphoria-season-three-to-begin-filming-january-2025-main-cast-return-3774678">在 7 月证实，该剧将于今年 1 月开始拍摄</a>，此前有大量<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/euphoria-season-three-heres-when-the-new-season-will-arrive-3531201">关于第三季推迟的</a>报道，再加上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/euphoria-actor-angus-cloud-has-died-aged-25-3475909">去年 8 月《幸福感》主演安格斯·克劳德 (Angus Cloud) 的惨死，雪上加霜</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3476729" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476729" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3476729" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new.jpg" alt="赞达亚·安格斯·云" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Zendaya-Angus-Cloud-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476729" class="wp-caption-text"> 《幸福感》由赞达亚和已故的安格斯·克劳德联合主演。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer/VF22/WireImage for Vanity Fair</figcaption></figure><p>这些延误显然足以让该剧的主演们感到困惑——斯威尼告诉<em>《NME》</em> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/sydney-sweeney-immaculate-euphoria-madame-web-snl-3603533">她“不知道我多久才能回家”</a> ，并表示当她回到剧组时，她感觉“就像在家里一样”。</p><p>与此同时，赞达亚今年早些时候表示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendaya-weighs-in-on-euphoria-delay-its-beyond-me-3619076">该剧的推迟“超出了我的承受范围”</a> 。</p><p>发表此评论之际<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendayas-alleged-feud-with-sam-levinson-explained-and-how-it-affected-euphoria-season-three-3777456">，有传言称赞达亚</a>从<i>《幸福感》</i>转而专注于<i>《偶像》</i> ，之后他和萨姆·莱文森之间的创作关系恶化——<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/hbo-the-idol-cancelled-after-just-one-season-3490069">这部剧受到了评论家的普遍批评，仅仅一季后就被取消了</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/zendaya-on-euphoria-season-three-the-time-jump-is-happening-3799956">Zendaya 在《Euphoria》第三季中发表的帖子：“时间跳跃正在发生”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff) 赞扬萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)、查理·XCX 和查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 举办的“艺术家发展夏季” https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-prases-sabrina-carpenter-charli-xcx-and-chappell-roan-for-artist-development-summer-3799943?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=杰克·安东诺夫赞扬萨布丽娜·卡彭特·查理·xcx 和查佩尔·罗恩的夏季艺术家发展Laura MolloySun, 06 Oct 2024 09:27:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3799943 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他们三人都拥有艺术家的共同经历，他们都在不断结晶，这就是你获得宝石的地方”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-praises-sabrina-carpenter-charli-xcx-and-chappell-roan-for-artist-development-summer-3799943">杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff) 赞扬萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)、查理·XCX (Charli XCX) 和查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的“艺术家发展之夏”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jack-Antonoff-Sabrina-Carpenter-Charli-XCX-and-Chappell-Roan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>赞扬了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">查理·XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>今年的工作，并表示“小子夏天”应该更名为“艺术家发展夏天”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">这是 Charli XCX 的世界，我们只是生活在其中：到目前为止“Brat”夏天的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>制作人参考了 Charli XCX 的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> ”专辑，该<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">专辑一经发行就成为一种流行文化现象</a>。在接受<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/jack-antonoff-taylor-swift-sabrina-carpenter-grammys-interview-1235792588/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard 的</em></a>新采访时，安东诺夫称赞 Charli、Carpenter 和 Roan 经过多年磨练艺术家技艺，在塑造 2024 年流行音乐方面发挥了重要作用。</p><p> “萨布丽娜、查理和查佩尔·罗恩——他们三人都有过共同的艺术家经历，他们都在不断结晶，这就是你获得宝石的地方，”他告诉该出版物。 “这就是成为一名艺术家的故事。这才是真正的艺术家发展。无论我们在技术、流媒体或其他领域处于什么位置，唯一的获胜方法就是创建自己的语言。”</p><p>安东诺夫在卡彭特的最新专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short N&#39;Sweet</a> ”中共同创作了四首歌，其中包括她的热门歌曲“Please Please Please”。在谈到她今年赢得赞誉时，他说：“萨布丽娜一直在悄悄成长，她的专辑变得越来越棒，她一直在磨练她的声音和表演。她并不是突然出现在舞台上的——她已经为此奋斗了十年。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenters-short-n-sweet-has-gone-platinum-3797928">卡彭特的《Short N&#39; Sweet》上个月被美国唱片业协会认证为白金唱片</a>，这意味着该唱片的销量已超过一百万张。根据 RIAA 的<a href="https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&amp;se=sabrina+carpenter#search_section" target="_blank" rel="noopener">记录</a>，这也使《Short N&#39; Sweet》成为她第一张达到这一里程碑的专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3799256" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799256" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799256" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024.jpg" alt="Sabrina Carpenter（图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for AEG）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799256" class="wp-caption-text"> Sabrina Carpenter（图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for AEG）</figcaption></figure><p>至于罗恩， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-her-previous-label-didnt-want-her-to-release-pink-pony-club-3792531">今年早些时候她透露，她的第一家唱片公司不希望她发行她的热门歌曲《Pink Pony Club》</a> ，尽管它后来成为了粉丝最喜欢的歌曲。</p><p> 2020 年，她通过大西洋唱片公司发行了这首单曲，但几个月后被该唱片公司放弃。去年，她通过 Island and Amusement Records 发行了首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/lollapalooza">The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess</a> 》，其中收录有《Pink Pony Club》，并成为她最受欢迎的热门歌曲之一。</p><p>从那时起，她的第一张专辑在发行近一年后就获得了英国冠军， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-congratulates-chappell-roan-on-chart-success-the-meteoric-rise-of-a-midwestern-princess-3782611">埃尔顿·约翰最近对此表示祝贺</a>。并且，在分享了单曲“Good Luck, Babe!”之后今年四月，这首歌在英国排名第四，并于六月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-sabrina-carpenters-stripped-back-cover-of-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-for-bbc-radio-one-live-lounge-3766709">在 BBC Live Lounge 中由 Sabrina Carpenter 翻唱</a>。</p><p> Lolla 代表证实，这位“Hot To Go”歌手名声大噪，今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roans-lollapalooza-set-is-among-the-festivals-most-attended-in-history-3781184">吸引了 Lollapalooza 历史上最大规模的日间观众</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3795517" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795517" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795517" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024.jpg" alt="查佩尔·罗恩（吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chappell-Roan-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795517" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-confirms-all-18-features-for-the-brat-remix-album-3799823">Charli XCX 最近确认了所有将在她的“Brat”混音专辑中亮相的艺术家</a>，该专辑的标题是“Brat，它完全不同，但仍然是brat”。将于 10 月 11 日发布，可<a href="https://charlixcx.lnk.to/bratcompletelydifferent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预存</a>。</p><p>迄今为止，这张专辑已经预览过与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/addison-rae">Addison Rae</a>合作的《Von Dutch》、与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">Lorde</a>合作的《Girl, So Confusing》、与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">Yung Lean</a>合作的《360》、与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>合作的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess</a> 》、以及与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">Troye Sivan</a>合作的《Talk Talk》。加上<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的口头发言。</p><p>这位“Guess”歌手现已透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">Bon Iver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tinashe">Tinashe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julian-casablancas">Julian Casablancas</a> 、BB Trickz、Bladee、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-japanese-house">The Japanese House</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jon-hopkins">Jon Hopkins</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a>将加入这张专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3798875" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798875" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798875" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff-lana-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff-lana-del-rey@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff-lana-